WEBVTT

00:14:55.938 --> 00:15:00.152
when the UN was trying to develop
a universal conception of human rights,

00:15:00.176 --> 00:15:02.780
the anthropologists all lined up and said,

00:15:02.804 --> 00:15:04.003
"This can't be done.

00:15:04.027 --> 00:15:07.597
This is a fool's errand. There is no
such thing as universal human rights."

00:15:07.931 --> 00:15:10.948
Think of how ethically
questionable that position is.

00:15:10.972 --> 00:15:16.333
Like, there's no way to say
that clitorectomies are a bad thing, say.

00:15:16.745 --> 00:15:22.671
It's pure delusion, the moment
you link morality to the well-being

00:15:22.695 --> 00:15:26.521
of conscious creatures, in general,
and people in particular.

00:15:26.545 --> 00:15:31.786
Once you draw the link between
human flourishing and morality,